<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tolerant-adj">tolerant <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'tɒlərənt/    美 /'tɑːlərənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>宽容的；容忍的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Luckily, my parents were <strong>tolerant of</strong> my choice of books.
幸运的是，我父母对我选择读什么书持宽容态度。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Instead of blaming the child who had broken the vase, she gave him a <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ smile and let him go.  （2014 湖北）<br />
A.cautious<br />
B.grateful<br />
C.tolerant<br />
D.wild  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. C  </p></div>